params.name: save_directory
params.description: Directory where the tokenizer files and the speaker embeddings will be saved (directory will be createdif it does not exist).

params.name: speaker_embeddings_dict_path
params.description: The name of the .json file that will contains the speaker_embeddings nested path dictionary, if itexists, and that will be located in pretrained_model_name_or_path/speaker_embeddings_directory.

params.name: speaker_embeddings_directory
params.description: The name of the folder in which the speaker_embeddings arrays will be saved.

params.name: push_to_hub
params.description: Whether or not to push your model to the Hugging Face model hub after saving it. You can specify therepository you want to push to with repo_id (will default to the name of save_directory in yournamespace).

params.name: kwargs
params.description: Additional key word arguments passed along to the push_to_hub() method.
